description:
The Great Sport Relief Bake Off - Series 1, Episode 4




The winners of the three heats bake a trio of biscuits and demonstrate their technical skills by preparing a batch of sausage rolls using puff pastry. In the final challenge, they must create a tiered cake before judges Mary Berry and Paul Hollywood decide who deserves to be crowned this year's champion. Last in the series.




Original Air Date: 13-Jan-2012
